{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FullDocumentReaderConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKit\/documentation\/KeyboardKit\/Proxy-Article"]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKit\/documentation\/KeyboardKit\/Proxy\/FullDocumentReaderConfiguration\/sleepInterval","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" sets how long to wait with any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subsequent operations when the text cursor has moved."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It’s needed because a proxy needs to pause before it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can access more text. A too short delay will cause a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"read to just return empty text, which will cause the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"operation to abort, while too long delays will cause","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the read operation to take longer."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The standard ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0.04"},{"type":"text","text":" sleep interval is tested to work"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on older devices, like iPhone 7, while newer devices"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use a much shorter interval like "},{"code":"0.02","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". You can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the predefined "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKit\/documentation\/KeyboardKit\/Proxy\/FullDocumentReaderConfiguration\/standard"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKit\/documentation\/KeyboardKit\/Proxy\/FullDocumentReaderConfiguration\/fast","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" configs."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKit\/documentation\/KeyboardKit\/Proxy\/FullDocumentReaderConfiguration\/endOfProxyAttempts","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" determines how many times"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to attempt to move the text cursor when reaching the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"beginning or the end of the proxy. This is needed to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"handle texts that have many line breaks, since these"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"line breaks can otherwise cause the operation to end."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The standard ","type":"text"},{"code":"10","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" attempts will make a proxy attempt","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to move the cursor that many times, but it will fail","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if there are more paragraphs. Using more attempts is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"however taking longer to complete."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"This configuration can be used to set up how to read","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the full document context of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UITextDocumentProxy"},{"type":"text","text":" ."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKit\/documentation\/KeyboardKit\/Proxy\/FullDocumentReaderConfiguration"},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"